dc_description_s: Copperplate print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the right. Relief shown by hachures. Includes 5 insets and legend. Eight sheets joined. 1 map: mounted on paper; 72 x 102 cm., folded in cover 19 x 14 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
